INSERT INTO blueprint_skill
                (
                    blueprint,

                    activity,

                    type_id,
                    level
                )
                SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                    $1::UUID[],
                    $2::SMALLINT[],
                    $3::INTEGER[],
                    $4::INTEGER[]
                )
                ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING

538eda4476509d5744bd2fac0db05528e2b73165.query:
INSERT INTO item
                (
                    type_id,
                    category_id,
                    group_id,
                    volume,
                    name
                )
                SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                    $1::INTEGER[],
                    $2::INTEGER[],
                    $3::INTEGER[],
                    $4::REAL[],
                    $5::VARCHAR[]
                )
                ON CONFLICT(type_id) DO UPDATE
                SET category_id = excluded.category_id,
                    group_id    = excluded.group_id,
                    volume      = excluded.volume,
                    name        = excluded.name
